plot_embedding

Source: R/plotting_functions.R
plot_embedding.Rd

Plot embedding of the expression matrix.

plot_embedding(
  expression_matrix,
  labels = NULL,
  method = "tsne",
  colors = RColorBrewer::brewer.pal(length(unique(labels)), "Set1"),
  seed = 1,
  point_size = 1
)

Arguments

expression_matrix

Input data frame.

labels

Input data frame.

method

Method to use for dimensionality reduction.

colors

Colors to use for the plot.

seed

Seed for the random number generator.

point_size

Size of the points.

Value

ggplot object

Examples

data("example_matrix")
samples_use <- 1:200
labels <- sample(
  c("A", "B", "C", "D", "E"),
  nrow(example_matrix[samples_use, ]),
  replace = TRUE
)

plot_embedding(
  example_matrix[samples_use, ],
  point_size = 2
)



plot_embedding(
  example_matrix[samples_use, ],
  labels,
  point_size = 2
)



plot_embedding(
  example_matrix[samples_use, ],
  labels,
  method = "pca",
  point_size = 2
)
